### IDE & Editor Local Configurations
# VS Code - ignore local settings but preserve shared config
**/.vscode/*
!**/.vscode/settings.json
!**/.vscode/tasks.json
!**/.vscode/launch.json
!**/.vscode/extensions.json
!**/.vscode/*.code-snippets
**/.vscode/*.local.*

# JetBrains IDEs - ignore local, keep shared
**/.idea/*
!**/.idea/*.xml
!**/.idea/.gitignore
!**/.idea/runConfigurations/
**/.idea/*.local.*

# Copilot & GitHub Copilot
**/.copilot/
**/.copilotignore
**/.github/copilot-instructions.md.local

# Codex CLI
**/.codex/config.local.toml
**/.codex/*.local.*

